<subSubSection id="11E3DCD4FFB8FFD4FCEEFB8AFA61FA9E" pageId="7" pageNumber="276" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="59468F5FFFB8FFD4FCEEFB8AFA61FA9E" blockId="7.[801,1452,1068,1284]" pageId="7" pageNumber="276">
<emphasis id="6B8D534DFFB8FFD4FCEEFB8AFA50FBDE" box="[839,1424,1068,1092]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="276">
Distribution and ecology. – 
<taxonomicName id="9EF9F4DCFFB8FFD4FBD6FB8AFA50FBDE" authorityName="Buerki, Callm., Munzinger &amp; Lowry" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Buerki, Callm., Munzinger &amp; Lowry" baseAuthorityYear="2020" box="[1151,1424,1068,1092]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Sapindaceae" genus="Lepidocupania" kingdom="Plantae" order="Sapindales" pageId="7" pageNumber="276" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="gracilipes">Lepidocupania gracilipes</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is endemic to Grande Terre, where it grows in gallery forest, continuous tall maquis (“maquis paraforestier”, see 
<bibRefCitation id="3D68F2AEFFB8FFD4FA92FBCAFCB6FB3E" author="MCCOY, S. G. &amp; JAFFRE, F." pageId="7" pageNumber="276" pagination="579 - 594" refId="ref12158" refString="MCCOY, S. G., T. JAFFRE, F. RIGAULT &amp; J. E. ASH (1999). Fire and succession in the ultramafic maquis of New Caledonia. J. Biogeog. 26: 579 - 594." type="journal article" year="1999">MCCOY et al., 1999</bibRefCitation>
for details), and thickets on (rocky) serpentine terrain, and sometimes along streams on alluvium (
<bibRefCitation id="3D68F2AEFFB8FFD4FB59FB0BFA48FB5E" author="TURNER, H." box="[1264,1416,1196,1220]" pageId="7" pageNumber="276" refId="ref12575" refString="TURNER, H. (1995). Cladistic and biogeographic analyses of Arytera Blume and Mischarytera gen. nov. (Sapindaceae) with notes on methodology and a full taxonomic revision. Blumea, Suppl. 9." type="book" year="1995">TURNER, 1995</bibRefCitation>
). It seems to be restricted to serpentine, hyper-magnesium brown soils. The species has been recorded from sea level to 
<specimenCount id="4FFF44D6FFB8FFD4FAFDFB4AFA61FA9E" box="[1364,1441,1260,1284]" pageId="7" pageNumber="276" type="generic">
<quantity id="9E0122BAFFB8FFD4FAFDFB4AFA5EFA9E" box="[1364,1438,1260,1284]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="276" unit="m" value="600.0">600 m</quantity>
.
</specimenCount>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
